narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: GMAN 140 01 was a good setting to learn german, especially for someone insecure of their knowledge. Herr Kavett's kind approach to teaching was well-received and has definitely improved my german.
I highly recommend if you are ready for this level of German. It was a low-stress but productive class.
It's a language course. Expect hear only German during class and also be prepared to only speak German as well. It's a good course if you are interested in learning more of the language and culture.
